losing at least a piece.}) (5... Nf6 6. exd5 Nxd5 7. Nxd5 Qxd5 8. Nf3 {It might
not look like much for White but in reality it is not so easy for Black to
develop in this position as the bishop on c8 is stuck.} 8... Bxc5 9. O-O O-O
10. Bf4 f6 11. Qe2 {Also Black's queen will be struggling to find a decent
square as it can be under several hits on d5.} 11... Qh5 12. Be4 {The queen is
